parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Detachment of A-Pillar Trim and Windshield Moulding
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The detachment of the A-pillar trim and windshield moulding can cause a loud noise, wind noise, and wind entering the vehicle, which can be distracting and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: The A-pillar trim and windshield moulding detach while driving
causing a loud noise
wind noise
and wind entering the vehicle. The trim pieces may fly off and potentially hit other vehicles or pedestrians.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rust on the aluminum hood can cause structural damage and potentially lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Rust bubbles and rust on the aluminum hood.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Abnormal Sound Coming from the Vehicle
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The abnormal sound coming from the vehicle can be distracting and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: An abnormal sound coming from the vehicle
which may be related to the detachment of the A-pillar trim and windshield moulding.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The detachment of the roof rack trim can cause a loud noise and potentially lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The roof rack trim detaches while driving
causing a loud noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the windshield trim can cause it to break off while driving, creating a safety hazard for the driver and other vehicles on the road.
symptoms: The windshield trim breaks off or becomes loose while driving
causing a rattling or flapping noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the exhaust system can cause carbon monoxide to enter the passenger compartment, leading to poisoning and potentially life-threatening consequences.
symptoms: A strong exhaust smell is present in the vehicle
and occupants may experience neurological symptoms such as headaches
dizziness
and nausea.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear camera can increase the risk of accidents and injuries, particularly when reversing or parking.
symptoms: The rear camera fails to function
and the screen displays a blank or distorted image.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inadequate horn can fail to alert other drivers or pedestrians, increasing the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The horn produces a low or weak sound
making it difficult for others to hear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the roof rack rails can cause them to detach while driving, creating a safety hazard for the driver and other vehicles on the road.
symptoms: The roof rack rails become loose or detach while driving
causing a rattling or clunking noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch hydraulic system can cause the clutch pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
the clutch pedal has a sudden loss of pressure
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the SYNC 3 navigation system can cause the system to malfunction, leading to driver distraction and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The SYNC 3 navigation system fails to function properly
causing errors or freezing.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the torque converter can cause the vehicle to shudder, hesitate, or lose power while driving, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle shudders or hesitates while driving
the vehicle loses power while driving
the vehicle has a rough idle
the vehicle has a delayed or incomplete acceleration
the wrench light or powertrain light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or shudder while driving, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power while driving
the vehicle hesitates or shudders while driving
the vehicle has a delayed or incomplete acceleration
the transmission slips or fails to engage
the wrench light or powertrain light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the PTU can cause the vehicle to shudder or hesitate while driving, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle shudders or hesitates while driving
the vehicle has a delayed or incomplete acceleration
the PTU warning light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical and heating system can cause the vehicle to experience intermittent electrical and heating system failures, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The display screen fails to turn on or shuts off
the wipers stop mid-swipe
the mirrors fail to adjust
the seat warmer fails to work
the floorboard heat fails to work
the auto start fails to work.
